name: Datascape Shell - Jiajia
text:
2+ Level 3 monsters
Once per turn: You can detach 1 material from this card, then target 1 face-up monster you control; it cannot be destroyed by battle until the end of your opponent's turn. Once per turn, after damage calculation, if this card battled an opponent's monster and you have 2 or more monsters with the same original Type and Attribute in your GY: You can banish that opponent's monster.
